urlLink A Missing Statistic: U.S. Jobs That Went Overseas : "A Missing Statistic: U.S. Jobs That Went Overseas By LOUIS UCHITELLE  Published: October 5, 2003   he job market finally showed some life in September, but not enough to sidetrack a growing debate over why employment has failed to rebound nearly two years after the last recession ended. The debate intrudes increasingly on election politics, but in all the heated back and forth, an essential statistic is missing: the number of jobs that would exist in the United States today if so many had not escaped abroad"